of the possibility of additive CNS effects (e.g., drowsiness, dizziness, lightheadedness, confusion) and counseled to avoid activities requiring mental alertness until they know how these agents affect them.', 'Synergism', 'Caution is advised when zonisamide is prescribed with other drugs that predispose patients to heat-related disorders, including carbonic anhydrase inhibitors and drugs with anticholinergic activity.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/177566/', '', 'Amisulpride, Pimavanserin', 'Lacosamide, Tinidazole, Simeprevir, Rosuvastatin, Sulfadiazine, Lactic acid, Mitapivat, Methazolamide, Clindamycin, Ciclopirox, Darunavir, More', 1767369485);
